            "folder": "Gg8SQFKssgHH6OUz",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
            "name": "Ghoul Whispers",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> A @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Paralyzed], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Restrained], or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Unconscious] creature is within the ghoul's reach</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The ghoul whispers dark thoughts and vile cravings into the creature's ears. The creature must save against the forbidden cravings curse.</p>\n<p><strong>Forbidden Cravings</strong> (curse) A creature can still eat and drink while sickened by this curse</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[will|dc:26|traits:curse]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effects (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Damage[2d6[void]] damage and the target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} until it consumes raw meat (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> as stage 2</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> as stage 2 unless the target has consumed raw meat in the past 24 hours, then it takes @Damage[4d6[void]] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} until it consumes raw meat;</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> if the creature has eaten raw meat in the past 24 hours, it dies and rises as a ghoul, if not, it returns to stage 4</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "ORC",
                    "remaster": true,
                    "title": "Pathfinder Monster Core"
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": "ghoul-ghoul-whispers",
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "auditory",
                        "linguistic",
                        "occult"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "SRFExdZZTEkIM9JJ",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Grisly Display",
            "sort": 700000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The ghoulrilla howls and claws at its flesh, flinging bits of matted fur, gristle, and rancid meat in a nauseating display. The ghoulrilla takes @Damage[1d6[slashing]] damage, and all creatures within @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] feet must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:23] save. While a creature is sickened by this ability, it is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] to the ghoulrilla.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creatures is unaffected and temporarily immune for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2}, and a piece of the ghoulrilla's body or rancid blood got into the creature's mouth, open wound, or otherwise infected them—the creature is exposed to forbidden cravings (see Ghoul Whispers).</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "emotion",
                        "fear",
                        "mental",
                        "visual"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
